        <h1 class="section-title">Content Guidelines</h1>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: March 19, 2024</p>

            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>These Content Guidelines are designed to help you understand what content is acceptable on GGShorts. By using our platform, you agree to follow these guidelines and help us maintain a positive and respectful community.</p>

            <h2>2. Prohibited Content</h2>
            <p>The following types of content are strictly prohibited:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Hate speech or discriminatory content</li>
                <li>Violent or graphic content</li>
                <li>Sexual content or nudity</li>
                <li>Harassment or bullying</li>
                <li>Spam or misleading content</li>
                <li>Copyright infringement</li>
                <li>Impersonation or fraud</li>
                <li>Illegal activities or content</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Content Quality Standards</h2>
            <p>To maintain a high-quality platform, all content should:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Be original and authentic</li>
                <li>Be relevant to gaming and entertainment</li>
                <li>Be properly categorized and tagged</li>
                <li>Have clear audio and video quality</li>
                <li>Include appropriate descriptions and titles</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Community Guidelines</h2>
            <h3>4.1 Respectful Interaction</h3>
            <p>All users should:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Treat others with respect</li>
                <li>Engage in constructive discussions</li>
                <li>Report inappropriate content</li>
                <li>Follow platform-specific rules</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>4.2 Content Moderation</h3>
            <p>We reserve the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Remove content that violates our guidelines</li>
                <li>Suspend or terminate accounts</li>
                <li>Report illegal activities to authorities</li>
                <li>Update these guidelines as needed</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>5. Copyright and Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>Users must respect intellectual property rights:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Only upload content you own or have permission to use</li>
                <li>Properly credit original creators</li>
                <li>Respect copyright laws and fair use guidelines</li>
                <li>Report copyright violations</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>6. Content Recommendations</h2>
            <p>For the best results, we recommend:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Creating original gaming content</li>
                <li>Using high-quality recording equipment</li>
                <li>Adding engaging descriptions and tags</li>
                <li>Interacting with your audience</li>
                <li>Following trending topics in gaming</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>7. Enforcement</h2>
            <p>Violations of these guidelines may result in:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Content removal</li>
                <li>Account warnings</li>
                <li>Temporary suspension</li>
                <li>Permanent account termination</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>8. Updates to Guidelines</h2>
            <p>We may update these guidelines periodically to reflect changes in our community standards and platform features. Users will be notified of significant changes.</p>

            <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about these guidelines or need to report violations, please contact us at:</p>
            <p>Email: content@ggshorts.com</p>
